text: In Jimmy Butler's debut, Sixers blow a 16-point 4th q lead at Orlando and lose. Jimmy was hesitant to take over and close. That must change. Embiid had his 1st career trip-dub but fell in love with jumpers late instead of attacking, shooting FTs. This team will grow from this.
Joel Embiid is the best player in the East. But he doesn't always choose the wisest shots.

If the Warriors trust DCousins health the second half of this season, they should trade Draymond. More trouble than he's worth. Salvage this season and increase chances KD stays, at least next year. Draymond called KD a name you can't take back.
Uh-oh, NOW what can I say about LeBron??? 9:30 E. Undisputed. FS1.
Is Tom Brady washed up? How impressive was LeBron passing Wilt? Next on Undisputed.
